sentences: Jessica R. Asis (born on December 24, 1978), professionally known by the names DJ Laila, Laila Chikadora, and Laila Chikadora Pangilinan, is a radio DJ and TV personality in the Philippines.
She is currently a radio DJ of 92.3 News FM and an entertainment reporter of News5.
